        In this Schedule –
            land means –
                    (a) permanent timber production zone land; or
                    (b) Crown land within the meaning of the Crown Lands Act 1976 ; or
                    (c) land owned by the Forestry corporation; or
                    (d) any other land owned by a State-owned company or Government Business Enterprise –
                but does not include any of the following:
